{"word":"Phenicia","slug":"phenicia","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Phenicia</b> Called also Phenice.<br/> Inhabitants of, descended from Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=15'>Gen 10:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=19'>Gen 10:19</a><br/> Called Zidonians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=18&verse=7'>Jdg 18:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=32&verse=30'>Eze 32:30</a><br/> Jews from, hear Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=8'>Mar 3:8</a><br/> Paul visits the churches in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=3'>Act 15:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=4'>Act 21:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27&verse=3'>Act 27:3</a>"}]}